::Prowl::

Kissing back as Iron Raptor deepens the kiss, Prowl slides his arms 
around her, feeling her bare skin on his palms. This was all new in a 
way: feeling her emotions, feeling what she felt along with what he 
felt, but he rather liked it..

His hands slide over her back to get a better hold of her, pressing 
her body to his and enjoying the feeling of it, his spark beating 
with love for her, combined with the love he felt from her.
